node.text: I thought I’d make a fun little video on my phone of making this delicious honey Focaccia and collecting the honey I used from my flow hive. it’s a great italian flat bread crispy on the top yet deeply soft and spongy inside yum….it can easily transition breakfast, brunch & amazing filled savoury sandwiches for lunch it’s on page 12 of my new book that you can be pre ordered now it’s out in a month ! All Very exciting it’s called Together I can’t wait to share it with you happy Sunday love Jamie o xxx
